===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|blessinge}}, {{m|enm|blessynge}}, from {{inh|en|ang|blētsung}}, {{m|ang|blēdsung|t=a blessing}}, equivalent to {{af|en|bless|-ing}}.

